              <img src="assets/img/Product_FaceX/Photo_10.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
              <img src="assets/img/Product_FaceX/Diagram_01.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
              <img src="assets/img/Product_FaceX/Photo_04.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
              <img src="assets/img/Product_FaceX/Photo_05.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
              <img src="assets/img/Product_FaceX/Photo_02.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
              <img src="assets/img/Product_FaceX/Photo_06.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
              
              

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 ml-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
              <div class="sticky-content">
                <h3 class="h3">Detachable Hull</h3>
                <!-- <p class="mb-4"><span class="text-muted">Design</span></p> -->

                <div class="mb-5">
                  <p>FaceX features a rigid detachable hull which houses a removable, disposable filter over the nose and mouth of the user. This project enabled further material exploration through the development of a magnetic silicone which snuggly seals around the face, and allows for easy attachment/detachment from the auxetic frame. </p>

                </div>

                
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-4 align-items-center">
          
